Ko da yake 'yan majalisar sun gabatar da wasu shawarwari, amma gwagwarmayar neman zama ɗaya ta ba wa shugaban tawagar, Elin Jones, babban aiki, kuma za ta gabatar da wannan doka a cikin makonni biyu.
