Tsarin majalisar dokokin Cromwell ya zama wanda ya gabata na tarihin tarihin tarihin
Cirewar wannan mutum-mutumi zai zama karma ga Cromwell da kuma halakar da wasu abubuwa na al'adu da addini a Ingila kamar yadda mabiyansa na puritan suka yi a lokacin yakin basasa na 16th karni.
Amma kungiyar Cromwell ta kwatanta shawarar Crick game da kawar da mutum-mutumi a matsayin tøys da eit ƙoƙari na rubuta game da tarihin.
John Goldsmith, shugaban kungiyar Cromwell, ya ce: "A cikin muhawara game da kawar da mutummutumai, ba makawa cewa siffar Oliver Cromwell a waje da fadar Westminster za ta zama manufa.
