Wataƙila Cromwell ba daidai ba ne zai zama hadaya ga ayyukan kakanninsa, Thomas, a ƙarni na baya.
Sir William Hamo Thorneycroft ta musamman wakiltar Cromwell ne shaida ga jama'a ra'ayoyi a karni na 19, kuma yana da wani ɓangare na tarihin tarihin mutum wanda mutane da yawa har yanzu suna ganin yana da daraja bikin.
Goldsmith ya ce wa The Sunday Telegraph: Cromwell ya kasance a karni na 19, kuma har yanzu a yau, ana kallon shi a matsayin mai kare majalisar dokokin kasar daga matsin lamba, kuma a cikin yanayinsa, ba shakka, yana da rinjaye ga mulkin mallaka.
