Ragowar guguwar Rosa ta kawo ruwan sama zuwa kudu maso yammacin Amurka
Kamar yadda aka annabta a cikin rahoton, hurricane Rosa ya raunana a kan ruwan sanyi a arewacin tekun Mexico.
Duk da haka, Rosa zai kawo ruwan sama na arewacin Mexico da kudancin yammacin Amurka a cikin kwanaki masu zuwa.
Rosa yana da ƙarfin iska har zuwa 136 km/h kuma yana da hadari na category 1 har zuwa karfe 05:00 na yammacin Amurka a ranar Lahadi, kuma cibiyar hadari ta kasance kilomita 620 kudu maso yammacin Punta Eugenia, Mexico.
Rosa za ta koma arewa a ranar Lahadi.
A tsakiyar lokaci, akwai wani ƙananan matsin lamba a kan Pacific Ocean wanda ke motsawa zuwa gabas zuwa yammacin Amurka, kuma Rosa ya zo kusa da Baja California a ranar Litinin a cikin wani mummunan yanayi na guguwa, kuma zai motsa zafi mai zafi zuwa arewa zuwa kudu maso yammacin Amurka.
Rosa zai kawo har zuwa 25 centimeters ruwan sama zuwa sassa na Mexico a ranar Litinin.
Yawan zafi na tropical zai yi aiki tare da ƙananan matsin lamba kuma ya haifar da ruwan sama mai yawa a kudu maso yammacin kwanakin nan.
A cikin gida, tsakanin 3 da 10 cm na ruwan sama na iya haifar da ruwa mai haɗari da kuma yiwuwar ƙetare ƙasar a cikin hamada.
Ruwa mai zafi zai haifar da ruwan sama tsakanin 5 zuwa 7 centimeters a kowace awa a wasu sassa na kudu maso yammacin Amurka, musamman a wasu sassa na kudu maso Nevada da Arizona.
Ana samun ruwan sama tsakanin 5 da 10 cm a wasu sassan kudancin Amurka; musamman a manyan sassan Arizona.
Ruwa mai haɗari zai iya faruwa saboda yaduwar ƙasa da ruwan sama na tropical.
Ana kiyaye shi a kan tafiya a cikin jeji a ƙafa saboda haɗarin ruwan sama na tropical.
Ruwa na iya haifar da raƙuman ruwa zuwa koguna masu gudana kuma hasken wuta da guguwa zasu kawo iska mai karfi da ƙura.
Ƙarƙashin matsin lamba na gaba zai kawo ruwan sama ga sassa na gabar teku a kudancin California.
Ana iya samun yawan ruwan sama na sama da centimeter 1, wanda zai iya haifar da ƙananan fitila da hanyoyi masu santsi.
Wannan zai zama ruwan sama na farko na kakar wasa a yankin.
Ana yin ruwan sama a Arizona a ranar Lahadi da yamma da kuma Litinin da safe, kafin ruwan sama ya tashi a ranar Litinin da Laraba.
Yankin Four Corners na iya jiran ruwan sama mai yawa a ranar Alhamis da Laraba.
Oktoba na iya shaida mummunan yanayin zafi a duk fadin Amurka yayin da Arctic ke samun sanyi, amma wurare masu zafi zasu kasance masu zafi.
Wani lokaci wannan yana haifar da bambancin yanayi, ko da tsakanin kananan yankuna.
Lahadi ya kasance misali na bambancin yanayin zafi a sassa na Amurka.
Akwai kusan digiri 20 na bambancin zafin jiki tsakanin Kansas City, Missouri, da Omaha, Nebraska, da kuma tsakanin St. Louis da Des Moines, Iowa.
A cikin kwanaki masu zuwa, za a yi ƙoƙari a lokacin rani don gina kansu da kuma sake yadawa.
Yawancin jihohin Amurka na tsakiya da gabashin suna tsammanin za su fara farawa a watan Oktoba, tare da digiri 25 zuwa sama daga kudancin manyan filayen arewa maso gabashin Amurka.
New York City na iya kaiwa digiri 25 a ranar Alhamis, wanda ya kai kimanin digiri 10 sama da matsakaici.
Amsar tsawon lokaci ta nuna cewa akwai yiwuwar samun yanayin zafi a gabashin Amurka a farkon rabin Oktoba.
Mutane sama da miliyan 20 sun kalli sauraron Brett Kavanaugh
A ranar Alhamis, mutane fiye da miliyan 20 sun ga shaidar Brett Kavanaugh a kotun koli ta Amurka da kuma matar da ta zarge shi da cin zarafin jima'i a shekarun 1980, Christine Blasey Ford, a tashoshi shida daban-daban na talabijin.
A lokaci guda, tattaunawar siyasa a kan batun ta ci gaba, tare da katsewa a cikin shirye-shiryen talabijin na yau da kullum na kamfanonin watsa shirye-shirye daban-daban don bayyana sabon abu a ranar Jumma'a: yarjejeniyar da Sanata Jeff Flake na Arizona ya cimma game da FBI a cikin mako mai zuwa don bincika zargin.
Ford ta shaida wa kwamitin kotun koli cewa ta tabbata da kashi 100 cikin dari cewa Kavanaugh ya umarce ta lokacin da ya sha giya kuma ya yi kokarin cire tufafinta a wani babban makaranta-ƙauye.
Kavanaugh ya ce, a lokacin wata hira mai ban mamaki, ya tabbata da kashi 100 cikin dari cewa ba zai faru ba.
A ranar Juma'a, mutane fiye da miliyan 20,4 ne suka ga wannan taron, a cewar Nielsen.
Kamfanin ya samu wannan lambar ta hanyar gano matsakaicin yawan masu kallo a CBS, ABC, NBC, CNN, Fox News da MSNBC.
Ba a bayyana adadin da aka samu daga wasu tashoshin da suka nuna wannan sauraron ba, ciki har da PBS, C-SPAN da Fox Business Network.
Nielsen kuma yana da matsala wajen ƙidaya masu kallo da ke kallon daga ofishin.
Don saka wannan a cikin hangen nesa, akwai irin wannan adadin masu kallo da ke kallon wasan karshe na kwallon kafa na Amurka ko kuma Oscar.
Masu watsa shirye-shiryen Fox News sun goyi bayan Kavanaugh, kuma tashar ta kasance mafi yawan masu kallo a rana tare da masu kallo miliyan 5,69, in ji Nielsen.
ABC ta kasance a matsayi na biyu da masu kallo miliyan 3.26.
CBS na da masu kallo miliyan 3,1, NBC miliyan 2,94, MSNBC miliyan 2,89 da CNN miliyan 2,52, Nielsen ya ce.
Mutane har yanzu suna sha'awar sauraron.
Flake ya kasance a cikin mayar da hankali a lokacin wasan kwaikwayo a ranar Jumma'a.
Bayan Flake, wanda mai tsaka-tsaki ne, ya bayyana cewa yana kan Kavanaugh, CNN da CBS sun yi fim da shi yayin da 'yan adawa suka yi kira gare shi a kan hanyar sauraron wani kwamiti mai hukunci a ranar Jumma'a.
Ya tsaya yana kallon kasa na mintuna da dama yayin da 'yan adawa suka yi masa magana a CNN live.
"Ina tsaye a gabanka", wata mace ta ce.
Kuna ganin yana gaya wa kasarmu gaskiya?
Waɗansu suka ce masa, "Kai mai iko ne, amma mata masu iko ba su da iko".
Flake ya ce ofishinsa ya bayyana kansa, kuma kafin ya shiga gidan, ya ce yana son ya kara daukaka a lokacin taron.
Rundunar watsa labarai ta nuna sauraron a talabijin lokacin da hukumar hukuma ta yi zabe don ko a kan zaben Kavanaugh zuwa majalisar dattawa da kuma kara zabe.
Amma Flake ya ce zai iya yin hakan ne kawai idan FBI ta binciki tuhumar Kavanaugh a cikin mako mai zuwa, abin da 'yan Democrat suka bukaci.
Flake ya kasance a gefe guda ya rinjayi bayan ya yi magana da abokinsa, dan majalisa da kuma sanatan Chris Coons.
Bayan ya yi magana da Coons da wasu 'yan majalisar dattawa bayan haka, Flake ya yanke shawara.
Flake ya yanke shawarar da ya tabbatar da cewa yana da iko, saboda ya bayyana cewa 'yan Republican ba za su iya yin zabe ba ga Kavanaugh ba tare da bincike ba.
