'Yan sanda sun yi gwagwarmaya da 'yan ta'adda na Catalonia a ranar tunawa da zaben 'yancin kai
An kama 'yan zanga-zangar shida a Barcelona a ranar Asabar bayan da 'yan zanga-zangar 'yancin kai suka yi tawaye da' yan sanda, kuma dubban wasu 'yan zanga-zangar sun yi zanga-zangar nuna rashin amincewa da 'yancin kai shekara guda bayan zaben da aka yi game da yiwuwar karbo daga Spain.
Wasu 'yan sanda sun tsare wasu 'yan ta'adda a lokacin da suka jefa ƙwai da kuma kayan da suka sanya a cikin titi, wanda yawanci ya cika da masu yawon bude ido.
A wannan lokacin, an sake fashewa a baya a rana, kuma 'yan sanda sun yi amfani da batons don hana su.
A cikin 'yan sa'o'i masu fafutukar raba gardama sun yi kira ga 'yan tawaye da suka yi watsi da 'yan tawaye, suna cewa, "Bari Spain ta rayu".
Rahotanni na gida sun ruwaito cewa an yi wa mutane goma sha huɗu magani don ƙananan raunuka bayan zanga-zangar.
Har yanzu ana buga kuri'un a yankin kuma mutane da yawa suna son samun 'yancin kai shekara guda bayan zaben 1 ga Oktoba, wanda Madrid ta kira ba bisa ka'ida ba, amma separatists a Catalonia suka yi bikin.
Yawancin masu jefa kuri'a sun yi murya don 'yancin kai, amma akwai ƙananan tashin hankali a tsakanin waɗanda ke adawa da 'yancin kai da kuma ƙin yin zabe.
A cewar hukumomin kasar, kusan mutane 1000 ne suka ji rauni a bara bayan da 'yan sanda suka yi kokarin hana zaben da kuma rikice-rikice da suka faru a yankin.
Ƙungiyoyin da ke da 'yancin kai sun kwana a cikin tanti a ranar Juma'a don hana zanga-zangar da ke goyon bayan' yan sanda na jihar.
Duk da haka, zanga-zangar ta tafi daga cikin dandamalin, amma an tilasta ta zuwa wani hanya.
Narcis Termes, mai shekaru 68, wani mai aikin lantarki wanda ya shiga zanga-zangar 'yan ta'adda tare da matarsa, ya ce ba shi da bege na samun 'yancin kai a Catalonia.
A bara mun samu daya daga cikin abubuwan da suka fi mu dadi.
Na ga iyayena suna kuka saboda farin ciki domin sun yi murya domin 'yancin kai, amma yanzu mun sake kasancewa, "in ji shi.
Ko da yake sun lashe zaben yanki a watan Disamba, jam'iyyar Catalan da ke da 'yancin kai na kokarin ci gaba da mulki a wannan shekara, yayin da yawancin shugabanninsu ke gudun hijira ko kuma a tsare yayin da suke jiran shari'arsu game da rawar da suka taka a cikin shirya zaben da kuma sanarwar 'yancin kai da ta biyo baya.
Joan Puig, wani mai shekaru 42 da haihuwa mai aikin injiniya wanda ya yi fim na zanga-zangar a kan wayarsa, ya ce 'yan siyasa a bangarorin biyu sun yi ta tayar da rikici.
"Tsananin ya kara ƙaruwa", in ji shi.
A ranar Asabar Oriol Junqueras, daya daga cikin shugabannin Catalonia tara da suka shiga cikin shari'o'in da ake ci gaba tun bara, ya bayyana cewa zai yi zaben majalisar Turai a shekara mai zuwa.
"Shin yin shuru a matsayin dan takarar a zaben Turai shine hanya mafi kyau na yin hukunci da koma bayan dabi'un dimokiradiyya da kuma zalunci da muka fuskanta daga gwamnatin Spain", in ji shi.
