Wannan shi ne ranar karshe ta ziyarar Erdogan a Jamus - wanda ake fatan zai gyara dangantakar kasashen biyu na NATO.
Kasashen sun kasance ba su da daidaituwa a kan hakkin dan Adam, 'yancin yada labarai da kuma rawar da Turkiyya ke takawa a cikin Tarayyar Turai.
Erdogan ya tafi Cologne don bude wani babban sabon masallaci.
Birnin shine gida ga mafi yawan mutanen Turkiyya a waje da Turkiyya.
'Yan sanda sun hana taron mutane sama da dubu 25 da suka taru a gaban masallacin saboda dalilai na tsaro, amma yawancin magoya bayan Erdogan sun taru don ganin shugaban kasar.
Daruruwan 'yan adawa da Erdogan - da yawa daga cikin Kurdawa - sun kuma yi zanga-zangar don ƙaryata Erdogan da manufofinsa da kuma shawarar da gwamnatin Jamus ta yanke game da so ya yi masa maraba a kasar.
Masu zanga-zangar sun nuna bambanci tsakanin 'yan Jamus na Turkiyya, wadanda suka dauki Erdogan a matsayin jarumi, da kuma wadanda suka dauka shi a matsayin autokrat.
Hadarin mota a Deptford, London: Wani mai siyar da motoci ya mutu bayan ya yi karo da mota
