Kanye West: Rapper ya canza sunansa zuwa Ye
Rapper Kanye West ya canza sunansa zuwa Ye.
Ya bayyana canjin sunan a Twitter a ranar Asabar, kuma ya rubuta: Halitta da aka sani da Kanye West.
West, 41, ya yi amfani da Ye a matsayin sunan sa na wani lokaci, kuma ya yi amfani da sunan a matsayin taken kundin sa na takwas, wanda ya saki a watan Yuni.
Canjin sunansa ya zo daidai kafin ya yi aiki a kan Saturday Night Live, inda yake jiran ya saki sabon album Yandhi.
Ya maye gurbin mawaƙa Ariana Grande a kan wasan kwaikwayon bayan da ta soke saboda dalilai na yanayi, in ji mai gabatar da shirye-shiryen.
Bugu da ƙari, ga taƙaitaccen sunan mai zane na yanzu, West ya bayyana cewa kalmar tana da ma'ana ta addini a gare shi.
Ina tsammanin kalmar ye ita ce kalmar da aka fi amfani da ita a cikin Littafi Mai Tsarki, kuma a cikin Littafi Mai Tsarki tana nufin du, West ya ce a farkon wannan shekara lokacin da yake tattauna taken album tare da mai watsa shirye-shiryen rediyo Big Boy.
Don haka ni ne kai, ni ne mu, mu ne.
Sunansa ya canza daga Kanye, wanda ke nufin kawai, zuwa kawai Ye - don nuna kyawawan abubuwan da muke yi, munanan abubuwan da muke yi, rikicewarmu, komai.
Wannan kundi yana nuna mana ko wanene mu.
Kanye yana daya daga cikin shahararrun rappers da suka canza sunansa.
Sean Combs ya fi sani da Puff Daddy, P. Diddy ko Diddy, amma a wannan shekara ya bayyana cewa ya fi son sunayen Love da Brother Love.
Jay-Z, wanda ya yi aiki tare da West a baya, ya canza rubutun sunan tare da kuma ba tare da haɗin kai da manyan haruffa ba.
Shugaban kasar Mexico na nan gaba ya yi alkawarin cewa ba zai tura sojoji zuwa ga fararen hula ba
Shugaban kasar Mexico, Andres Manuel Lopez Obrador, ya yi alkawarin cewa ba zai taba tura sojojinsa ba ga 'yan ƙasa, kuma kasar za ta yi bikin tunawa da shekaru 50 da zubar da jini da aka yi wa ɗalibai.
Lopez Obrador ya yi alkawarin ranar Asabar a Tlatelolco Plaza cewa ba zai taba amfani da sojojin ba don yaudare mutanen Mexico.
Ranar 2 ga watan Oktoba na 1968, sojojin sun harbe 'yan zanga-zangar lumana suka kashe mutane 300, a lokacin da ƙungiyoyin ɗalibai na hagu suka yada a Latin Amurka.
Lopez Obrador ya yi alkawarin tallafawa matasa na Mexico ta hanyar ba da tallafi na wata-wata ga dalibai da kuma bude wasu jami'o'i kyauta.
Ya ce rashin aikin yi da rashin samun ilimi sun sa matasa su shiga kungiyoyin masu aikata laifi.
Amurka ta kamata ta ninka yawan zuba jari a fannin fasaha
Da yake kasar Sin ta kara aiki da hankali na wucin gadi, Amurka ta kamata ta ninka zuba jari a bincike a kan wannan batu, in ji mai zuba jari da kuma mai amfani da wucin gadi Kai-Fu Lee, wanda ya yi aiki ga Google, Microsoft da Apple.
Bayanin da ya yi ya zo ne bayan da sassa daban-daban na gwamnatin Amurka suka bayyana kansu game da ilimin kere kere, ko da yake Amurka ba ta da wata dabarar amfani da ilimin kere kere.
A lokacin da kasar Sin ta gabatar da shirin a shekarar da ta gabata, tana da burin zama na 1 a fannin fasaha ta zamani a shekarar 2030.
"Hadin kasafin kudin bincike akan ilimin kere kere zai zama kyakkyawan farawa, saboda sauran kasashen suna baya ga Amurka, kuma muna neman ci gaba a fannin ilimin kere kere", in ji Lee.
A ninka kudi zai iya ninka damar da za a samu ci gaba mai girma a fannin fasaha a Amurka, Lee ya shaida wa CNBC a wata hira da aka yi da shi a wannan makon.
Lee, wanda ya wallafa littafinsa AI Superpowers: China, Silicon Valley and the New World Order a wannan watan ta hanyar kamfanin buga littattafai Houghton Mifflin Harcourt, shi ne babban darektan gudanarwa (CEO) na Sinovation Ventures, wanda ya zuba jari a daya daga cikin manyan kamfanonin fasaha na kasar Sin, Face++.
A shekarun 1980 ya yi aiki a Jami'ar Carnegie Mellon tare da tsarin fasaha wanda ya buga mafi girma mai kunnawa na wasan Othello, kuma daga bisani ya yi aiki a matsayin shugaban Microsoft Research kuma ya kasance shugaban Google a China.
Lee ya amince da gasar fasaha ta farko da Amurka ta shirya, kamar Defense Advanced Research Projects Agency's Robotics Challenge kuma ya tambayi lokacin da za a yi gasar ta gaba, don haka ya kasance tare da gano masu hangen nesa na gaba.
"Masana kimiyya a Amurka dole ne su yi aiki tukuru domin samun tallafi daga gwamnati", in ji Lee.
"Ba China ce ke daukar shugabannin ilimi ba, manyan kamfanoni ne", Lee ya ce.
Facebook, Google da sauran kamfanonin fasaha sun dauki dalibai masu kyau daga jami'o'i su yi aiki a kan fasaha na zamani a cikin 'yan shekarun nan.
Lee ya ce canje-canje a cikin manufofin baƙi na iya taimakawa Amurka don ƙarfafa bincike kan ilimin fasaha.
"Ina ganin cewa daliban digiri na biyu a fannin ilimin kere kere za su samu izinin zama na atomatik", in ji shi.
Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta wallafa shirin ta na gaba na fasaha a watan Yuli na 2017.
Kungiyar kimiyya ta kasar Sin ta kasa tana ba da kudade ga daliban makarantun kimiyya, ba kamar kungiyar kimiyya ta Amurka da sauran kungiyoyin gwamnati ba wajen raba kudade ga masu binciken Amurka, amma ingancin aikin ilimi ya fi kasa a kasar Sin, in ji Lee.
