LeBron ya fara wasa a Lakers a ranar Lahadi a San Diego
Lokaci na jira zai zo ga magoya baya da ke son ganin LeBron James ya fara wasan kwallon kwando a Los Angeles Lakers.
Kocin Lakers Luke Walton ya sanar da cewa James zai buga wasan a gasar gabanin kakar wasa a ranar Lahadi, a kan Denver Nuggets a San Diego.
Amma tsawon lokacin da zai yi wasa bai riga ya yanke shawara ba.
"Zai zama fiye da minti daya kuma ƙasa da 49," Walton ya sanar a shafin yanar gizon Lakers.
Dan jaridar Lakers, Mike Trudell, ya yi zargin cewa James zai iya taka leda na dan lokaci.
Bayan horo a wannan makon, an tambayi James game da tsare-tsarensa na Lakers na kakar wasa ta gaba.
"Ba na bukatar wani waƙar farko a wannan mataki na rayuwata don in kasance a shirye", ya ce.
Trumps West Virginia Rally Time, YouTube
Shugaba Donald Trump ya fara wani babban harin yakin neman zabe a Wheeling, West Virginia.
Wannan shi ne na farko daga cikin tashoshi biyar da Trump ya shirya a mako mai zuwa, ciki har da tashoshi a wurare masu kyau kamar Tennessee da Mississippi.
Tare da tabbatar da kuri'un da ke jiran za a zaɓa don cika ofishin da Kotun ta bayar, Trump ya yi niyyar gina goyon baya ga zaɓen tsakiyar lokaci mai zuwa tun lokacin da 'yan Republican ke cikin haɗari don rasa iko akan majalisa lokacin da za a ba da kuri'u a watan Nuwamba.
A wane lokaci ne Trump zai kasance a West Virginia a yau da dare, kuma ta yaya za ku ga hakan a yanar gizo?
An shirya taron Trump a Wheeling, West Virginia zuwa karfe 19:00 na dare, Asabar 29 ga Satumba, 2018.
Za ku iya ganin tarin Trump na West Virginia a kan layi a ƙasa, ta hanyar watsa shirye-shiryen YouTube.
Trump zai iya ɗaukar wannan makon sauraron Brett Kavanaugh, wanda aka nada a gaban kotun, wanda ya damu da zargin cin zarafin jima'i, tare da amincewar da majalisar dattawa ta yi masa a mako guda yayin da FBI ke bincike.
Amma babban burin wannan tarin tarin shine taimaka wa 'yan Republican su hadu da zaben watan Nuwamba kuma su sami wani lokaci (drivepower).
Wannan shine dalilin da yasa yakin neman zaben shugaban kasa Trump ya ce wadannan taro guda biyar na mako mai zuwa suna nufin karfafa masu sa kai da magoya bayan da 'yan Republican ke kokarin karewa da fadada rinjayen da suke da su a majalisar dattawa da majalisar wakilai, a cewar Reuters.
"Sarrafawa da majalisar dokoki yana da matukar muhimmanci ga tsarinsa cewa shugaban zai yi tafiya zuwa jihohi da yawa kamar yadda zai yiwu yayin da muke shiga cikin wannan lokacin yakin neman zabe", in ji wani mai magana da yawun yakin neman zaben Trump wanda ya ki sanar da Reuters.
An shirya don Wesbanco Arena a Wheeling, taron na yamma zai iya kawo magoya baya daga Ohio da Pennsylvania da kuma janye ɗaukar hoto daga Pittsburgh media, a cewar West Virginia Metro News.
Asabar ne karo na biyu a cikin wata na karshe da Trump ya ziyarci West Virginia, jihar da ya lashe da fiye da kashi 40 cikin dari a shekarar 2016.
Trump yana kokarin taimakawa dan takarar majalisar dattijai na West Virginia, Patrick Morrisey, wanda ake nema a zaben.
"Ba alama ce mai kyau ga Morrisey cewa shugaban kasa ya zo ya yi ƙoƙari ya ba shi wani alkawari a cikin ƙididdigar ra'ayi", in ji Simon Haeder, wani masanin siyasa a Jami'ar West Virginia, a cewar Reuters.
