Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump ya yi magana ne a ranar Laraba da ta gabata game da kudaden da China Daily ta biya a cikin rajistar Des Moines - babbar salsavicin jihar Iowa - bayan da ta zargi kasar Sin da kokarin shiga cikin majalisar dokokin Amurka a ranar 6 ga watan Nuwamba, wani bashi da kasar Sin ta ƙi.
