Rashin shigar da Rheinland-Pfalz, jagorancin sabon frigates na Baden-Wuerttemberg, yanzu an gabatar da shi zuwa farkon rabin 2019, a cewar Die Zeit-avisa, wanda ya ba da labarin wani mai magana da yawun soja.
Jirgin ya kamata ya shiga cikin jirgin ruwa a shekarar 2014, amma matsalolin da suka shafi isarwar sun shafi al'amuran da suka shafi aikin.
