Trump zai iya sake yin taro da Rosenstein, in ji fadar White House
Taron Donald Trump da ya yi da shugaban kasa Rod Rosenstein zai iya sake dawowa cikin mako guda yayin da ake ci gaba da gwagwarmayar da ake yi da shugaban kasa Brett Kavanaugh, fadar White House ta ce a ranar Lahadi.
Rosenstein ya kula da aikin da majalisar musamman ta Robert Mueller ta yi, wanda ke nazarin rikice-rikicen zaben Rasha, haɗin kai tsakanin masu taimaka wa Trump da Rasha da yiwuwar hana adalci na shugaban kasar.
