Palu babban birnin Sulawesi ne, kuma yana kan iyakar bakin teku a yammacin Sulawesi. Yawan jama'a a shekarar 2017 ya kai 379,800.
Birnin ya yi bikin cika shekaru 40 da girgizar ƙasa da tsunami suka auku.
Donggala wani yanki ne wanda ya wuce fiye da kilomita 300 tare da iyakar arewa maso yammacin tsibirin.
A shekara ta 2017, yankin, wanda ya fi ƙasa da lardin, ya kai kimanin mutane 299,200.
Fishing da gardsdrift sune abubuwan da ke faruwa a tattalin arzikin Sulawesi ta tsakiya, musamman a yankin Donggala.
