Masu gabatar da kara na tarayya a New York suna son hukuncin kisa ga Sayfullo Saipov, wanda ake zargi da harin ta'addanci wanda ya kashe mutane takwas -- wani laifi mai wuya wanda ba a yi ba a jihar saboda laifin tarayya tun 1953.
Saipov (30) ya yi amfani da motar haya daga Home Depot don kai hari kan wani motar hawa a kan West Side Highway a Lower Manhattan a watan Oktoba, inda ya kori 'yan sanda da masu hawa a kan hanya.
