Harin ya bukaci tsari da kuma tunani, 'yan wasan sun ce, kuma sun bayyana yadda Saipov ya kai hari a matsayin mai ban tsoro, mai ban tsoro da kuma lalata.
Sayfullo Habibullaevic Saipov ya haifar da rauni da asarar dangi da abokai na Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Ann-Laure Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erlij, Hernan Ferruchi, Hernan Diego Mendoza da Alejandro Damian Pagnucco, an rubuta a cikin bayanin kula.
