Lokaci na ƙarshe da aka yanke hukuncin kisa a cikin wani shari'ar tarayya a New York shine a 1953 ga Julius da Ethel Rosenberg, ma'aurata da aka kashe bayan da aka yanke musu hukuncin kisa don yin leken asiri ga Soviet Union a lokacin yakin basasa shekaru biyu da suka gabata.
