Sabuntawa a kan dinoflagellate: An rage yawan taro a Pinellas, Manatee da Sarasota
Rahoton da aka fitar daga hukumar kula da kifi da dabbobi ta Florida (FWC) ya nuna cewa yawan adadin dinoflagellate a yankin da ke kusa da Tampa Bay ya ragu.
A cewar FWC, an ruwaito cewa akwai rashin daidaituwa a cikin ci gaban da ke faruwa a yankunan Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Charlotte da kuma yankin Collier - wanda ke nuna raguwar yawan ci gaban.
Ci gaban dinosaur yana gudana fiye da kimanin kilomita 200 a kan rairayin bakin teku daga arewacin Pinellas zuwa kudancin jihohin Lee.
Akwai yankunan dinosaur da ke kusa da gabar teku a Hillsborough, kusan kilomita 16 daga gabar teku, amma idan aka kwatanta da makon da ya gabata, akwai yankuna da yawa.
Dinoflagellate an lura da su a Pasco.
An ruwaito matsakaicin taro a Pinellas a makon da ya gabata, ƙananan taro a bakin tekun Hillsborough, ƙananan taro a Manatee, matsakaicin taro a bakin tekun Sarasota, matsakaicin taro a Charlotte, babban taro a Lee da ƙananan taro a Collier.
Har yanzu ana samun rahotanni game da irritation a cikin hanyoyin iska a Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Lee da Collier.
Ba a bayar da rahoton tashin hankali a arewa maso yammacin Florida ba a makon da ya gabata.
